name: ancient guardian skull warrior in hyrule castle
description:
so! For the past 2 months I have been busy with the legend of zelda breath of the wild game on Nintendo Switch. I love that game and this is my interpretation of the enemy link, a skeleton with armor and his body emitting smoldering fire. I hope this character can appear in that game. this is my imagination. thanks

3007 x 3661 px | 300 dpi 2021
